OL,3,CScotland's safety put at risk by
OL,4,CWestminster's armed forces cuts ` SNP
OL,6,FThe SNP has accused Westminster of
OL,7,Fputting Scotland's safety at risk.
OL,9,FAnalysis by the House of Commons
OL,10,FLibrary, commissioned by the party,
OL,11,Fshows the size of the UK armed forces
OL,12,Fhas been cut by every Labour and Tory
OL,13,Fgovernment for nearly half a century.
OL,15,FIt shows the Army is now less than
OL,16,Fhalf the size it was in the 1980s.
OL,18,FWhen Margaret Thatcher came to power
OL,19,Fin 1979, the UK's armed forces had
OL,20,Faround 315,000 active personnel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782544686
OL,3,CScotland's safety put at risk by
OL,4,CWestminster's armed forces cuts ` SNP
OL,6,FThat fell to 210,800 by the time of
OL,7,Fthe 1997 Labour government, 191,710
OL,8,Fwhen the Tories came to power in 2010,
OL,9,F138,121 when Sir Keir Starmer became
OL,10,FPrime Minister in May 2024, and
OL,11,F137,966 by April this year.
OL,13,FThe size of the Army has been cut by
OL,14,Faround half over the same period from
OL,15,F156,000 to 74,368, the Royal Navy has
OL,16,Fbeen reduced from 73,000 to 32,516,
OL,17,Fand the Royal Air Force has been cut
OL,18,Fby almost two-thirds from 86,000 to
OL,19,F31,082, the SNP said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
