CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782544686
OL,3,CScotland's safety put at risk by
OL,4,CWestminster's armed forces cuts ` SNP
OL,6,FThe analysis found the number of armed
OL,7,Fforces personnel based in Scotland has
OL,8,Falso fallen, from 19,016 in 1979 to
OL,9,F9,740 in 2025.
OL,11,FAccording to the research, the number
OL,12,Fof Royal Navy ships fell from 89 at
OL,13,Fthe turn of the millennium to 57 by
OL,14,F2025, while the number of destroyers
OL,15,Fwas cut from 11 to six. The number of
OL,16,Ffrigates has also reduced, from 21 to
OL,17,F11, and the number of submarines is
OL,18,Fdown from 16 to nine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
