OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782544686
OL,3,CScotland's safety put at risk by
OL,4,CWestminster's armed forces cuts ` SNP
OL,6,FOverall, spending on defence has been
OL,7,Fcut in half as a proportion of GDP
OL,8,Fbetween the 1980s and today.
OL,10,FIn 1979, spending was 4.6% of GDP,
OL,11,Ffalling to 2.7% by 1997, 2.5% by 2010
OL,12,Fand 2.4% by 2025.
OL,14,FSNP Westminster leader Dave Doogan
OL,15,Fsaid: "The Labour Government is
OL,16,Ffailing to take national security
OL,17,Fseriously enough following decades of
OL,18,FWestminster cuts to our armed forces,
OL,19,Fwhich have left the UK increasingly
OL,20,Fvulnerable.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
