OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782544686
OL,3,CScotland's safety put at risk by
OL,4,CWestminster's armed forces cuts ` SNP
OL,6,F"Every Labour Party and Tory
OL,7,Fgovernment, for more than half a
OL,8,Fcentury, have made increasingly deeper
OL,9,Fcuts to our armed forces ` slashing
OL,10,Fthe size of the Army, Navy and RAF,
OL,11,Freducing Scottish regiments, depleting
OL,12,Fequipment, and cutting the number of
OL,13,Fcombat vehicles, naval ships and
OL,14,Faircraft.
OL,16,F"By failing to deliver the investment
OL,17,Fneeded, Westminster is putting
OL,18,FScotland's safety at risk.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
