OL,3,CScotland's safety put at risk by
OL,4,CWestminster's armed forces cuts ` SNP
OL,6,F"Keir Starmer lost two defence
OL,7,Fministers, and his own job, over his
OL,8,Flong-delayed and underfunded plans.
OL,10,F"As he heads to the exit door, it is
OL,11,Fvital that the next UK prime minister
OL,12,Furgently gets a grip, delivers the
OL,13,Finvestment required and ensures
OL,14,FScotland gets its fair share.
OL,16,F"The SNP has consistently called for
OL,17,Fmore investment in conventional
OL,18,Fdefence capabilities, and more support
OL,19,Ffor our forces, but instead
OL,20,FWestminster has decimated them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
