OL,3,CScotland's safety put at risk by
OL,4,CWestminster's armed forces cuts ` SNP
OL,6,F"At a time of global crisis and
OL,7,Finstability, we cannot afford any more
OL,8,FWestminster dithering and delays.
OL,10,F"As Scotland marks Armed Forces Week,
OL,11,Fthe SNP is urging the UK Government to
OL,12,Ffinally deliver the funding our armed
OL,13,Fforces need."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the Ministry of
OL,16,FDefence said: "Scotland is a defence
OL,17,Findustrial powerhouse.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@MO]xD@OOU
