OL,6,F"In 2024/25, the MoD directly spent
OL,7,Fmore than #2 billion in Scotland,
OL,8,Fsupporting 11,800 industry jobs and
OL,9,Finvesting in world-class shipbuilding,
OL,10,Felectronic systems and submarine
OL,11,Ftechnology which protects our
OL,12,Fpersonnel and allies.
OL,14,F"Scotland's biggest shipyards are full
OL,15,Fas a direct result of the significant
OL,16,Fprogramme of work we have under way.
